description:
Danny recaps the most recent episode of The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured a trip to Tahoe and Kathy making Kyle plug in her fan. Danny also touches on the Potomac trailer, the FRIENDS reunion, and a chilling apartment issue that jeopardized an important artifact.
